org.apache.flink.runtime.operators.util

类 BloomFilter.BitSet

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.flink.runtime.operators.util.BloomFilter.BitSet
  • 封闭类:
    BloomFilter

    public class BloomFilter.BitSet
extends Object
    Bare metal bit set implementation. For performance reasons, this implementation does not check for index bounds nor expand the bit set size if the specified index is greater than the size.
